{
  "texts": [
    "The strong performance of Speech LLMs in these paralinguistic and non-linguistic tasks is particularly significant, considering that most Speech LLMs are based on encoders that are primarily trained for ASR.",
    "Their ability to generalize effectively to tasks beyond the scope of traditional speech recognition demonstrates the considerable potential of Speech LLMs.",
    "This suggests that their capabilities are not confined to a narrow set of speech tasks, but extend across a broader range of complex perception and cognition tasks.",
    "b) Multitask Capabilities of Speech LLMs: The table also highlights the impressive multitask capabilities of Speech LLMs, as evidenced by their consistent performance across multiple tasks.",
    "Notably, Kimi-Audio achieves an average RPS of 0.92, reflecting its robust multitask performance across its evaluated tasks."
  ]
}